description:
794 E 7th St APT K, South Boston, MA 02127 is a condo home that contains 1,152 sq ft and was built in 2000. It contains 2 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. This home last sold for $1,130,000 in June 2024. 
 
The Zestimate for this house is $1,146,600. The Rent Zestimate for this home is $4,271/mo.
